OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start then turning
OL,6,Fcloudy over Orkney with showers
OL,7,Fspreading east, then mainly dry and
OL,8,Fbright in the afternoon. A lot of dry
OL,9,Fand sunny weather for Shetland but the
OL,10,Fodd sharp shower developing in the
OL,11,Fafternoon. Light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA bright evening with the odd
OL,14,Fshower around. Clear spells overnight
OL,15,Fwith further showers passing through
OL,16,Ffrom the west. Becoming breezy over
OL,17,FShetland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
