OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA mixture of bright spells
OL,6,Fand showers, turning heavy and perhaps
OL,7,Fthundery later. Mainly light south-
OL,8,Fwesterly winds but fresh at times over
OL,9,FShetland.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FOvernight showers clearing then a dry,
OL,13,Fbright start Thursday before cloud and
OL,14,Frain spread northeast. Sunshine and
OL,15,Fshowers on Friday then mainly dry and
OL,16,Fbright Saturday. Breezy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
